description._content:
Since a couple of year, the winner signs 3 tennis balls after the match. Then hit them in the crowd.... We got two broken arms yesterday night! (just kidding hahaha). But seriously Sharapova do a great job for this..and as you can see here with her marvelous smile..she does enjoy it as much as the fans ;-)

Uncrop shot.. i wish i had the full hand..but still good emotion and focus..

description._content: I’m continuing to explore colors in nature and shot this beautiful scene at Alouette Lake in British Columbia during the Flickr Island meet up. I'm currently traveling across the whole USA, making stops in Texas, Colorado, New Mexico, Arizona, Utah, California, Oregon, Seattle and British Columbia.
